    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/9dd528567abe9532c30853c396df3cbd.poster.avif?t=1703049476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/9dd528567abe9532c30853c396df3cbd.webm?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/9dd528567abe9532c30853c396df3cbd.mp4?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《三元方块》是一款受俄罗斯方块和石头剪刀布启发的休闲益智游戏。游戏里的操作对象均为随机生成的三元方块组，每个方块组都由分属于石头、剪刀和布类型的三个方块组成。在方块组叠放时，它会跟下面的方块产生一定的相互作用。这种相互作用的结果由方块类型所决定，使得游戏更有趣且更具挑战性。<br><br>本游戏像俄罗斯方块的地方是，游戏在每个回合都会生成一个会向游戏面板底部掉落的三元方块组。玩家可以对方块组进行移动和旋转操作，以控制方块组掉到底部或其他块上的堆叠位置和方位。因此游戏的操作方式跟俄罗斯方块基本一样。<br><br>但与俄罗斯方块很不同的是，在三元方块组进行堆叠时，方块组里的方块和它下面的方块会产生一些额外的操作。取决于方块的类型，方块组方块可能会跟它下面的方块产生相消或替换的操作，并且发生方块相消之后，剩余的块可以继续向下掉落和堆叠。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/42e0a4ecc46a327f9cc0f23319ddbc1c.poster.avif?t=1703049476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/42e0a4ecc46a327f9cc0f23319ddbc1c.webm?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/42e0a4ecc46a327f9cc0f23319ddbc1c.mp4?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《三元方块》支持三种游戏模式：休闲，常规和挑战，以及两种升级模式：行清除和全清除。这些模式决定了方块组的掉落速度和升级时的速度增加方式。它们也决定全清升级模式下的初始块的生成行数。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/97337848ceca89834ed677ed1755f16a.poster.avif?t=1703049476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/97337848ceca89834ed677ed1755f16a.webm?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/97337848ceca89834ed677ed1755f16a.mp4?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏既支持单人玩家模式，也支持双人玩家模式。其双人模式既支持两个玩家在同一电脑上分屏玩，也支持两个玩家在局域网内用不同的设备玩。而且游戏的双人模式还支持两个子模式：平行和对抗模式。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/5ae719c120e6ea964f9fd965ba1807a6.poster.avif?t=1703049476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/5ae719c120e6ea964f9fd965ba1807a6.webm?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/5ae719c120e6ea964f9fd965ba1807a6.mp4?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《三元方块》支持两种电脑玩家，分别对应易难水平。玩家可以选择跟电脑玩家对玩，也可以让一个电脑玩家自己玩，或两个电脑玩家对玩。<br><br>玩得开心！另外游戏还提供了一系列不错的动画背景供你欣赏！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/a6996fe9c5dd2b2f72019df64ca8b4af.poster.avif?t=1703049476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/a6996fe9c5dd2b2f72019df64ca8b4af.webm?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/a6996fe9c5dd2b2f72019df64ca8b4af.mp4?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/a14ecf3d22a37ecdb32a0ef6008e5f89.poster.avif?t=1703049476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/a14ecf3d22a37ecdb32a0ef6008e5f89.webm?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/a14ecf3d22a37ecdb32a0ef6008e5f89.mp4?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/62609120ea2be6d10906e5bfdef55221.poster.avif?t=1703049476\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/62609120ea2be6d10906e5bfdef55221.webm?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579270/extras/62609120ea2be6d10906e5bfdef55221.mp4?t=1703049476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
